features: File Folders: Pack of 100 high-quality manila folders designed for letter-sized documents (8.5 x 11 inches). Provide a perfect fit for your paperwork.

Assorted Colors: Experience the convenience of our assorted color pack – a vibrant selection of five colors. Organize your documents effortlessly with a color-coded system, making it easy to locate specific information.

1/3 Cut Tab: Navigate through your files seamlessly with the 1/3 cut tab feature. This thoughtful design allows easy labeling, making it simple to categorize and retrieve documents efficiently. Stay organized and in control with these user-friendly folders.

Premium Paper: Crafted from premium paper, these folders offer a blend of durability and sophistication. The high-quality material not only ensures longevity but also provides a sturdy foundation for your important documents, making these folders a reliable choice for professional and personal use.

Ideal Choice: Whether you're managing paperwork at the office, coordinating classroom materials, or organizing important documents at home, our manilla folders are versatile enough to meet your diverse needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars High Quality, Sturdy, Expandable
reviews.reviewText: This is a great pack of sturdy 1/3 cut letter size file folders. I was almost out of file folders to use in our home cabinet, so when I saw these offered, I thought I would try them. They give you a variety of colors so you can separate and label based on subject matter, if desired. The colors look nice - they aren't super bright, but instead more muted which is very attractive and makes them look more upscale. The biggest benefit is they expand well at the bottom providing a lot of space and strong support. So they fit a lot and are durable, making them more practical and useful than regular manila file folders that don't hold much. I'm very happy with them.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars good quality plus box makes for convenient storage
reviews.reviewText: Who doesn’t need extra file folders? These are just what you expect in a good ol’ file folder. Not in the least flimsy, 3 positions for labels. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Basic, practical product
reviews.reviewText: These file folders are made of cardstock that's a little bit thicker and heavier than the last batch of folders I bought. They have the tabs in three different locations so that they can be lined up in a filing cabinet without blocking each other. They come in a very sturdy cardboard box that will make them easy to store.I bought the traditional manila color, and am now a little sorry that I didn't order the pastel colors. In hindsight I see they would have been useful for keeping track of the various projects I use folders for. But even without that feature, these will be very useful. I can always use colored labels or stickers to identify groups. I am the president of a small volunteer organization and, when we're busy, I go through file folders as if they were candy, so I'm delighted to have them.
